{"id": "art-84", "label": "Art. 84", "title": "Art. 84: Reprezentarea convenţională a persoanelor juridice", "slug": "art-84", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 84: Reprezentarea conven&#355;ional&#259; a persoanelor juridice </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_102347105\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1366\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_102347105\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Persoanele juridice pot fi reprezentate\nconven&#355;ional în fa&#355;a instan&#355;elor de judecat&#259; numai prin\nconsilier juridic sau avocat, în condi&#355;iile legii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1460441507\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1365\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1460441507\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>[textul din Art. 84, alin. (2) din cartea I, titlul II,\ncapitolu